{"tid":372649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國濫藥情況嚴重　怪華企網上售毒","createTime":"2017-08-24T12:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T14:03:00.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5677f427b12567fa43c7b29d12a57e55f9caa923","tid":372649,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"美國濫藥情況嚴重　怪華企網上售毒 (18:26)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170824/s00005/1503568950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170824%2Fs00005%2F1503568950864&d=XVmCOPbwgKlZqwi1%2FIL3dNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=a59b99e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170824%2Fs00005%2F1503568950864&h=4085d412\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170824/s00005/1503568950864</a><br />\n<br />\n美國多個州份濫藥情況愈趨嚴重，每年有數萬人因為過量藥物致死或永久傷殘，執法部近年拘捕毒販人數卻連年下降，原來青少年近年傾向在網上郵購毒品。有藥物監管機構近日發表報告，直斥部分中國公司在網上出售美國當局管制藥物，最多人郵購的是強效類鴉止痛劑芬太尼（Fentanyl）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國有傳媒測試發現，多間中國公司在網上出售芬太尼，部分公司聲稱可以直接郵寄到府上。美國緝毒局（DEA）亦表示近年發現的「禁藥郵包」大多來自中國，部分不法商人接貨後會進一步加工改變化學成分，企圖避開檢測。<br />\n<br />\nDEA去年已組成14人小組研究打擊郵寄受管制藥物，外電曾多次報道，小組代表跟北京開會商討合作打擊跨國販毒。對於再有美國傳媒報道事件，北京回應稱美國將國內濫藥問題完全歸咎中國並不合理，重申中國有誠意而且一直致力打擊濫藥問題。"},{"pid":"3ab4d805bf26fde67e8eceff6b7a030e238fd278","tid":372649,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:51:58.000Z","msg":"Synthetic drug真係好危險"},{"pid":"8cb18f0c6574d30b2901ac3a1e0e2e6ce291ab3a","tid":372649,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現代版鴉片戰爭"},{"pid":"d92cb25549fde569c394aca5d2c7cdd24bfd2684","tid":372649,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"Mr white <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada54dc7e5c71676d15e2dc592f4a5f705c6f4b4","tid":372649,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢單唔係好耐啦咩"},{"pid":"bcc6bba0732fd8d31a6ea9af67e1a65e30a1dd0b","tid":372649,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢單唔係好耐啦咩</blockquote><br />\n支那唔合作"},{"pid":"7cc236b99da90766bffcfaae06026672785b63e2","tid":372649,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mr white <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}